<div class="w-100">
 <div class="row">
    <div class="w-100 shop_about_editor_panel"></div>	    
 </div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="card  w-100" style="margin: 0.8rem; padding: 1rem;">
	<div class="row">
		  <div class="col w-100 text-left profile-field-title" >Название магазина</div> 
	</div>
	<div class="row input-group">
  	   	  <div class="col shop_name" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem!important;">
		  	  <input type="text" id ="shop_name"  
 	  	 	  placeholder = 'Введите название магазина '
			  class="form-control" value="{{shop.name}}">
		 </div>
	</div>	
	<div class="row">
		  <div class="col w-100 text-left profile-field-title" >Галерея изображений</div> 
	</div>
      <div class="card">
	  <div class="row" style="padding: 1rem;">
           <div class="col-sm-4">
	        <div class="shop_about_page_btns w-100"> 
		      <form id="fileupload" name="fileupload">  	  	   
			<button class="btn mt-auto p-2 float-right btn-sm btn-red profile-image-change">
			  <i class="fas fa-image"></i>
			  <input id="photofile" name="photofile" type="file"  accept=".jpg, .jpeg, .png"  name="files[]" multiple style="opacity: 0; width: 100%; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0;">
			  Добавить картинку
			</button>
		      </form>
	        </div>		
              </div>
	    <div class="col-sm-8 about-images-gallery" ></div> 
 	   </div>
	<div class="row input-group">
	    <div class="col" style="margin: 0.5rem 0.5rem;">
	        <span class="about-images-gallery-error"></span>
	   </div>
	</div>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col callout callout-info" style="margin: 1rem;">
			<p>Из галереи вы можете их добавить в текст описания вашего магазина.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
     </div>
	<div class="row">
		  <div class="col w-100 text-left profile-field-title" >Описание магазина</div> 
	</div>
	<div class="row input-group">
                 <div class="col shop_description" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem!important;">
			<textarea  id="shop_description" 
 	  	 	  placeholder = 'Введите описание магазина '
			  rows=3 class="form-control editor-textarea"  >{{shop.description}}</textarea>
		</div>
	</div>	
	<div class="row">
		  <div class="col w-100 text-left profile-field-title" >Адрес магазина</div> 
	</div>
	<div class="row input-group">
  	  	 <div class="col shop_address" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem!important;">
			<input type="text" id ="shop_full_address"
 	  	 	  placeholder = 'Введите адрес магазина '
			 class="form-control" value="{{shop.address}}">
		</div>
	</div>	
	<div class="row">
		  <div class="col w-100 text-left profile-field-title" >Координаты на карте</div> 
	</div>
	<div class="row input-group">
  	  	 <div class="col shop_latitude" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem!important;">
			<input type="text" id ="shop_latitude"
 	  	 	  placeholder = 'Широта'
			 class="form-control" value="{{shop.latitude}}" style="max-width: 20rem;">
		</div>
	</div>	
	<div class="row input-group">
  	  	 <div class="col shop_longitude" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem!important;">
			<input type="text" id ="shop_longitude"
 	  	 	  placeholder = 'Долгота'
			 class="form-control" value="{{shop.longitude}}" style="max-width: 20rem;">
		</div>
	</div>	

	<div class="row">
		  <div class="col w-100 text-left profile-field-title" >Телефон магазина</div> 
	</div>

	<div class="row input-group">
  	  	 <div class="col shop_address" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem!important;">
			<input type="text" id ="shop_phone" 
 	  	 	  placeholder = 'Введите телефон магазина '
			 class="form-control" value="{{shop.phone}}"  style="max-width: 20rem;">
		</div>
	</div>	

    </div>
</div>
</div>




<script src="/main/pages/telegram/jobs/js/shop_about_editor.js"></script>